                    <p rend="center">
                        <hi rend="italic">Protocol of Signature</hi>
                    </p>
                    <p>The Treaties, Conventions, Agreements, Protocol and Declarations of even date
                        may be signed until midday on September 13, 1919.</p>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Done</hi> at Saint-Germain-en-Laye, the tenth day of
                        September one thousand nine hundred and nineteen.</p>
